snippet.title: Furmins on PS Vita
snippet.description:
Furmins for PS Vita finds players attempting to guide a bunch of adorable and lovable creatures across cunningly designed levels by rearranging a variety of items, as well as using bumpers and conveyor belts in real-time with well-coordinated precision.
